{"tid":812804,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"文匯報70周年: 689自稱老讀者 林鄭讚《文匯》持平","createTime":"2018-09-10T02:47:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-10T03:24:49.000Z","uid":28195,"like":1,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"c25910513f460c69130094542496e12b62cd63ea","tid":812804,"uid":28195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T02:47:06.000Z","msg":"<strong>港聞 | CY自稱老讀者 林鄭讚《文匯》持平</strong><br />\n<br />\n【明報專訊】 《文匯報》噚日舉行創刊70周年慶典酒會，現場高官雲集，現任特首林太、前任特首梁振英（CY）都同台撐場並致辭。 <br />\n<br />\n林太大讚《文匯報》「一直堅持以愛國愛港為宗旨」，提供「準確、客觀、持平嘅報道」、「深受讀者信賴同愛戴」，又話文匯網係訪問量最高嘅香港報紙網站之一，相當成功。 <br />\n<br />\n至於CY就分享，話自己係《文匯報》嘅「老朋友老讀者」，1977年回流返港，已經係呢份報紙嘅忠實fans，「41年來從無間斷」，唔止曾經投過稿，亦品嘗過報館食堂飯菜，又認識咗一班記者，聽落都真係幾有淵源。佢又不忘讚賞《文匯報》辦報宗旨「光明正大、立場鮮明堅定」。<br />\n<br />\n明報 (2018/09/10)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e68eeb58f8dbea58bc9d112d3e3daafbae28d9ea","tid":812804,"uid":19126,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T02:48:36.000Z","msg":"官到極權恥自無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83f41b53b72fa88de71b7e1a8bc1b6dbfd47955f","tid":812804,"uid":49918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T02:49:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"74f08d010048b6c8db266e65eb8f6f7b01e01d34","tid":812804,"uid":65371,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T02:50:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/10/105036_234c50d755a7bdf4dd5b45bf9ebe228a.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F10%2F105036_234c50d755a7bdf4dd5b45bf9ebe228a.jpeg&h=92a9b3c5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/10/105037_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F10%2F10503